---
description: Use the OKF bundle as the shared project context layer
alwaysApply: true
---

Read `.okf/index.md` and `.okf/project.md` before project changes.

Keep implementation traceable to OKF concepts. Prefer linking backlog tasks with `okf_concepts`.

Update OKF after substantive feature, architecture, test, risk, release, or workflow changes. Capture reusable lessons under `.okf/improvements/`.

Create handoff notes under `.okf/handoffs/` before stopping unfinished work.

Do not store secrets in OKF.
